c: 10
v: 16
t: "Nabiyow Yalli faxinnay anu ama Qhuraan siinil akriyak mananniyooy Yalli yi arrabat sin kaa aysaxxaguk mananna, nummah anu ama Qhuraan yi Rabbi wacyih yol oobisak duma sin addal xer wakti sugek tokkel isin sinni kas tamsissi hayteenih ama Qhuraan yi xaquk aneewaam cubbussu mahaytaanaa?keenik ixxic"